{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928100/extras/08-Screenshoot.png?t=1732440609\" /> <br>&quot;Oasis&quot; is a relaxed environmental strategy game, where players transform the barren sandy land into a prosperous and balanced ecosystem by planting various plants, providing living spaces for various organisms, and bringing life back to the dead world.<br><br>You need to plan your money reasonably to purchase the plants and environmental materials needed for sand control. <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928100/extras/01-Buy.png?t=1732440609\" /><br><br>Planting plants and arranging environmental materials can bring you income, which can be used to buy more plants and environmental materials. <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928100/extras/02-Plant.png?t=1732440609\" /><br><br>Planting different types of combinations of plants on a plot can produce different landforms and ecosystems.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928100/extras/04-Forest.png?t=1732440609\" /> <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928100/extras/06-Grassland.png?t=1732440609\" /><br><br>The combination of landforms and ecosystems will attract specific animals to come and live. <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928100/extras/05-Animals.png?t=1732440609\" /><br><br>Oasis has a lush hand-drawn pixel environment, pleasant music, and an ambient soundscape filled with atmosphere, giving people a quiet and meditative experience. You can also use the screenshot function to retain your unique sand control results. <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/app